<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The $_options array in the Zend_Ldap class is not declared, ie the following is missing</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
protected $_options;
</code></pre>

<p>or</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
protected $_options = array();
</code></pre>

<p>This isn't critical as PHP allows the arbitrary instantiation of class members at run-time however I don't think the default "public" visibility is appropriate.</p>

